description: The Republic of Ireland will not move forward into Phase 4 of its roadmap, the taoiseach confirms.
title: Coronavirus: Ireland puts brakes on easing lockdown amid 'real concern'
title_page: Coronavirus: Ireland puts brakes on easing lockdown amid 'real concern' - BBC News
maintext: The news that the country will not move forward comes amid concerns about a rising number of new cases of the virus - particularity in young people - since lockdown eased and the Republic of Ireland opened up again.
